comments.body: Abundant in the area. Found by a pond.

observation.description:
ANPC Keys Identification:

Asteraceae: Inflorescence with ray and disk florets

Keys to Asteraceae: 
- Achillea(white ray florets, flowers not strap-shaped, round-topped clusters; involucral bracts; small ray florets)
